	(text_box "3.3 V to 6 V synchronous boost converter supplying the LT3042 LDO stage.\nTPS61086 switching at 1.2 MHz (fixed frequency, PWM/PFM selectable via MODE). Integrated 2.5 A / 0.13 Ω power switch. Output voltage set via FB resistor divider. Input/output decoupling, soft-start, and loop compensation network. Test points: +3.3V_IN, +6V_OUT, FB, COMP."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 73.66 113.01 0)
		(size 57.15 12.72)
		(margins 1.4287 1.4287 1.4287 1.4287)
		(stroke
			(width -0.0001)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type none)
		)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(thickness 0.381)
				(bold yes)
				(color 0 0 0 1)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "631cc992-1e6e-4a87-a84d-c4d64535fb2a")
	)
	(text_box "AD7190 24-bit sigma-delta ADC front-end for Wheatstone bridge acquisition.\nDifferential inputs on SENSE± and OUT± lines with RC input filtering. SPI interface (CS, DIN, DOUT, SCLK, SYNC). External 4.9152 MHz crystal clock. Dual-supply decoupling (+5VA analog / +3.3V digital). P-MOS drive gate for load cell excitation control. Test points on all critical analog and digital nodes."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 279.4 109.22 0)
		(size 45.72 5.08)
		(margins 1.4287 1.4287 1.4287 1.4287)
		(stroke
			(width -0.0001)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type none)
		)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(thickness 0.381)
				(bold yes)
				(color 0 0 0 1)
			)
			(justify left top)
		)
		(uuid "971f0c48-6726-412d-badf-cee82cbffedd")
	)
	(text_box "Low-noise 5 V analog supply for ADC front-end (AVDD).\nLT3042 ultralow-noise LDO regulator (PSRR > 75 dB). Input: +6V from boost stage. Output: +5VA regulated via RSET = 50 kΩ (ISET = 100 µA). Solid tantalum capacitor on SET pin for noise suppression. Power-Good monitoring via PGFB divider. Test points: VIN, VOUT, SET, PGFB, PG."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 176.53 82.53 0)
		(size 58.42 5.1)
		(margins 1.4287 1.4287 1.4287 1.4287)
		(stroke
			(width -0.0001)
			(type solid)
		)
		(fill
			(type none)
